":56698,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T12:05:26.000Z","msg":"只要蘋果日報一日仲係唱衰樓市，港樓都會繼續GoGoGo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5eda66f627c75d3cc2484e806c956f76c88b51e","tid":784434,"uid":153236,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T12:13:56.000Z","msg":"過往香港股市大跌之後一年內有冇試過啲樓唔跌？"},{"pid":"4e0a76adc2146f4381c2482c73bb116df2a52ad7","tid":784434,"uid":34612,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T12:15:33.000Z","msg":"樓市長線升值，這點我不懷疑，但樓市同樣有升跌周期，這點毋庸置疑<br />\n<br />\n同意呢樣野"},{"pid":"e7218237c15cb44ed2a2756a984cbc63b80a7982","tid":784434,"uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dcb33f8352424b1355289356feaf06f9883ad78f","tid":784434,"uid":35746,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T12:01:08.000Z","msg":"你唔住,大把人住<br />\n<br />\n係囉黎炒果D先會跳樓"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T12:21:02.000Z","msg":"要自住，都要每月俾得起管理費，維修費 否則釘契（早排執達吏追數 發現死去多年屍體）"},{"pid":"8f2121de217b6aa5ea8aeaa7fb6d875c30aff23e","tid":784434,"uid":153236,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4e0a76adc2146f4381c2482c73bb116df2a52ad7","tid":784434,"uid":34612,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T12:15:33.000Z","msg":"樓市長線升值，這點我不懷疑，但樓市同樣有升跌周期，這點毋庸置疑<br />\n<br />\n同意呢樣野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:03:45.000Z","msg":"因為銀紙會不斷貶值，長遠黎講資產先可以唔俾通賬蠶食<br />\n<br />\n但如果出現通縮，例如好似日本咁就未必apply"},{"pid":"398b79fdf58a7863add464344ad89c0bf440c198","tid":784434,"uid":95201,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5f1137df655b7485f8cdc20a0e79c9473cf040ef","tid":784434,"uid":185449,"like":15,"dislike":5,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T11:13:49.000Z","msg":"股票你升跌都極其量係一紙股權書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但樓無論升跌都可以要黎住人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:14:59.000Z","msg":"97年，03年，08年唔洗住？<br />\n唔係話要做淡友，而係當好多人當樓係投資商品，而唔係單單拎黎住既時候，你認為真係有永遠唔跌既時候？如果樓價上升到租金回報率跌到得番2厘，買樓錢我剩買reits收4厘好過啦"},{"pid":"727e3efabed2bc145c7727284be3192387628ca1","tid":784434,"uid":8328,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"4e0a76adc2146f4381c2482c73bb116df2a52ad7","tid":784434,"uid":34612,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T12:15:33.000Z","msg":"樓市長線升值，這點我不懷疑，但樓市同樣有升跌周期，這點毋庸置疑<br />\n<br />\n同意呢樣野"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:28:57.000Z","msg":"長線升值？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n今次大跌之後唔會再有北水carry，亦無美國放水推高資產價格，香港樓質素加上transaction cost，根本唔係good investment<br />\n<br />\n再講剛需只係媒體加地產佬吹出黎，97, 03一樣有咁多人，相同供應量(計埋地產佬hold住未賣啲貨)<br />\n<br />\n唔好再咁天真以為LTV低就無事，從來銀行都係睇cashflow，黎緊經濟唔駛爆，只要轉向扯高失業率，你3個月供唔到就成街銀主盤<br />\n<br />\n總之呢一兩年買咗樓嘅各位，我真係恭喜你啊"},{"pid":"ca695b2f7727b7ab7a5e41164a5f0863dfee4426","tid":784434,"uid":51041,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:34:15.000Z","msg":"就算樓跌3成<br />\n仍然係不合理範圍之內&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"f0bf5a1926e7e20997b5a94ade6f6a3f7eea4813","tid":784434,"uid":58046,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ca695b2f7727b7ab7a5e41164a5f0863dfee4426","tid":784434,"uid":51041,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:34:15.000Z","msg":"就算樓跌3成<br />\n仍然係不合理範圍之內&hellip;&hellip;"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:46:13.000Z","msg":"所以應該超過3成"},{"pid":"daeb353f2e432e84e32d660d73c00fa81871964a","tid":784434,"uid":34612,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"727e3efabed2bc145c7727284be3192387628ca1","tid":784434,"uid":8328,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"4e0a76adc2146f4381c2482c73bb116df2a52ad7","tid":784434,"uid":34612,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T12:15:33.000Z","msg":"樓市長線升值，這點我不懷疑，但樓市同樣有升跌周期，這點毋庸置疑<br />\n<br />\n同意呢樣野"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-08-18T13:28:57.000Z","msg"